name: 24" Tigereye Necklace
description: This is a 24" necklace with 6mm Tigereye beads to front with chain to the back. Has Lobster claw closure. Has a triangular shaped focal to front. Has 1/2" earrings.     According to gemstone lore Tigereye is for optimism, peacefulness, and clarity.

name: 20" Fire Agate Necklace
description: This is a 20" necklace made with 14mm Fire Agate beads and silver plated chain links. Some have diamond cutting. It has a hook and eye closure. The earrings are 1 1/2".    According to gemstone lore agate is for balance, inspiration, and perceptiveness.

name: 17" Blue Goldstone
description: This is a 17" necklace made with 8mm Blue Goldstone beads to front with 3mm beads to back. Has 40mm focal to front with angel spacers on each side. Has heart shaped toggle closure. Has 1/2" oval earrings with silver plated backs. Look at the picture and you can see the flash that goldstone is famous for.

name: 20" Yellow Dragon Vein Agate Necklace
description: This 20" necklace is made with 8mm yellow dragon vein agate beads with fluted metal spacers and oval pendant made with brown concrete with cross and genuine Mexican Fire Opal in it. It has lobster claw closure. Earrings are 1/2" in length.     According to gemstone lore agate is for balance, inspiration, and perceptiveness.

name: 20" 3-strand freshwater pearl necklace
description: This is a 20" 3-strand necklace made with 6mm freshwater pearls with Happily Ever After in Antique Gold. 1 word on each strand. Has brown suede leather to back with antique gold toggle closure. Earrings are 1" long. According to gemstone lore pearls stand for purity, faith, and sincerity.
